        googleRating: 4.8,
        tripadvisorRating: 4.7
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        name: "Alla Marina",
        category: "Boutique Guesthouse",
        village: "Riomaggiore",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520250497591-112f2f40a3f4?q=80&w=2670&auto=format&fit=crop",
        intro: "Modern comfort inside a 13th-century shell, right where the sea meets the street.",
        description: "Alla Marina manages to be both historic and contemporary. The building is one of the oldest in the village, but the interiors are bright, clean, and thoughtfully designed. It's located at the very end of the main street, making it the perfect base for those who want to be steps away from both the water and the best restaurants.",
        giuliaComment: "The staff here are what make the difference. They treat you like a guest in their own home. I always notice the light in these rooms—it reflects off the harbor water and dances on the ceilings in the afternoon.",
